movies.title: Cloud Princess
movies.shortDescription:
Director Statement
The emotional core of this short film is the unyielding strength of its spirit. Ordinary people and animals made extraordinary by their resilience and firmness of purpose, which overcome not only challenges, but weakness and error as well. At the end of their journeys, we understand the real meaning of life and how we need to need to live together with a sense of Ubuntu, Oneness.

Adapted from the book, Nelson Mandelas Favourite African Folktales, the folktale ultimately builds a sense of hope and upliftment. The aim is to make a powerful and entertaining short film, with resonant images and emotionally charged stories. A crisp editing style, digital effects and a soundtrack that captures the high and low moments in the lives of the characters that will enhance the engaging narrative and create a memorable dramatic experience for any audience.
